    b. TELEGRAM PLATFORM COMPLIANCE AND ABUSE LIABILITY.

       The Work is designed to interact with the Telegram platform via
       the Telegram Bot API, the MTProto user-bot API (via pyrofork), and
       related services. You acknowledge and agree that:

       (i)   You are solely responsible for ensuring that Your use of the
             Work complies fully with Telegram's Terms of Service, Privacy
